            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1663092326631-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, return the <strong>golden</strong> <strong>pork belly </strong>to the dish, skin-side up</p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook, uncovered, for an initial 50 min – this is your <strong>pork belly stew</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1663092331763-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1663092331763-x400.jpg",
