            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>crispy pork belly</strong> from the dish and slice into 3<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>slices per person on a clean board</p><p>To serve, top the stew with the<strong> pork belly slices</strong> with the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
